        <div class="story-content">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>The charity: water story begins with its founder, Scott Harrison, a former nightclub promoter, who, after witnessing the devastating effects of dirty water in West Africa, felt compelled to start a nonprofit. Launched in 2006, charity: water is built on the principle of transparency, directing 100% of donations to fund clean water projects while covering operating costs separately. The organization has funded over 186,000 water projects, serving more than 20.3 million people by bringing clean, safe water to communities worldwide</p>
        </div>
